        "text": "πῦρ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " to be kindred = fire the emblem of the Spirit as a purifier. They are right as to the affinity but not as to the function. The function in both cases is judicial. John refers to the Holy Wind and Fire of Judgment It is, however, not impossible that Lk. read an evangelic sense into John’s words.",
